ed":"2026-07-02T12:21:04.503Z","id":"projects","tags":[],"title":"Projects","url":"https://minnduc.github.io/projects"},{"_indieweb":{"type":"article"},"content_html":"<p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-12r7f95\">You can see my CV <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1t3KDAn6dXVzjnIzYiL4v0U0oWeQsA8dW/view?usp=sharing\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer external\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>","date_modified":"2026-07-02T00:00:00.000Z","date_published":"2026-07-02T12:21:04.503Z","id":"resume","tags":["Resume","Welcome","About"],"title":"Resume","url":"https://minnduc.github.io/resume"},{"_indieweb":{"type":"article"},"content_html":"<h1 id=\"about-me\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1nwhtfo\"><a href=\"#about-me\">About me!</a></h1> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1f6pdhf\">My name is Minh Duc.</p> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-anpe9i\">You can pronounce it as “Min” and “Duc” - where “Duc” sounds like “Duck”. The name “Duc” carries profound meanings in Vietnamese culture, representing virtues like morality, talent, and leadership qualities, which I strive to embody in both my personal and professional life.</p> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-ms3j0y\">I am currently a third-year Information Technology student at the University of Information Technology (UIT), VNU. As I progress through my academic journey, I’m building a strong foundation in computer science fundamentals while exploring cutting-edge technologies that shape our digital future. And, I aim to become an MLOps Engineer in the future.</p> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-z16r6z\">Besides, I love learning Math, code, computer, games, League of Legends, manga, swimming, gym and orca.</p> <h2 id=\"about-this-blog\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1592ket\"><a href=\"#about-this-blog\">About this blog</a></h2> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1a1574o\">This blog simply shares my life journey.</p>","date_modified":"2026-07-02T00:00:00.000Z","date_published":"2026-07-02T12:21:04.503Z","id":"welcome","tags":["Hello World","Welcome","About"],"title":"Hello World","url":"https://minnduc.github.io/welcome"},{"_indieweb":{"type":"article"},"content_html":"<h2 id=\"introduction\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-ccveyw\"><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></h2> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1u7r46r\">This project is a deep learning-based application for recognizing Japanese characters in manga images. It helps extract and identify Japanese text from manga pages, supporting language learning and text digitization.</p> <h2 id=\"result\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-rm05h\"><a href=\"#result\">Result</a></h2> <p>Experimental Results of Text Recognition Methods<img alt=\"alt text\" class=\"rounded-lg my-2\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/mangaocr/Result.png\"></p> <p>Convergence Curves of SVTR<img alt=\"alt text\" class=\"rounded-lg my-2\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/mangaocr/train_SVTR.png\"></p> <p>Convergence Curves of SVTR<img alt=\"alt text\" class=\"rounded-lg my-2\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/mangaocr/train_CRNN.png\"></p> <p>Convergence Curve of TrOCR<img alt=\"alt text\" class=\"rounded-lg my-2\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/mangaocr/trOCR_train.png\"></p>","date_modified":"2026-06-20T00:00:00.000Z","date_published":"2026-07-02T00:00:00.000Z","id":"projects/mangaocr","image":"/assets/MangaOCR.png","summary":"Deep learning-based Japanese character recognition in Manga.","tags":["Coursework","Project","Deep Learning","OCR"],"title":"Japanese Character Recognition in Manga (Manga OCR)","url":"https://minnduc.github.io/projects/mangaocr"},{"_indieweb":{"type":"article"},"content_html":"<h2 id=\"introduction\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-ccveyw\"><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></h2> <p data-svelte-h=\"svelte-q7r444\">EcoWaste is a web application that manages waste information and uses OpenAI APIs to classify waste from images, helping users sort waste correctly and raise environmental awareness.</p> <h2 id=\"demo-video\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1qz2hh8\"><a href=\"#demo-video\">Demo video</a></h2>   <div data-testid=\"general-observer\"></div> <br>","date_modified":"2025-05-26T00:00:00.000Z","date_published":"2025-07-02T00:00:00.000Z","id":"projects/ecowaste","image":"/assets/EcoWaste.png","summary":"Waste management system with AI-powered waste classification.","tags":["Project","AI","Website"],"title":"EcoWaste","url":"https://minnduc.github.io/projects/ecowaste"}],"language":"en-US","title":"Minh Duc","version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1"}